How to install Gray:

1. If glut libraries are not installed:

sudo apt-get install freeglut3 freeglut3-dev

2. If zlib not installed:

sudo apt-get zlib1g-dev

3. Compile program:

from Gray home directory

source GRAY_ENVIRONMENT_VARIABLES.sh
cd workspace
source buildGray.csh

4. Executable code is workspace/RayTraceKd/debug/Gray. A symbolic link is also created in the Gray home directory